<plot>William S. Hart dreams he is called before the War Council as an expert gunman and is directed to 'remove' the Kaiser. In Berlin, he sees the Kaiser on a rocking horse, in a rage over the 4th Liberty Loan. Bill fires and the Kaiser falls. Bill is captured and is about to be bayoneted when he wakes up.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?007999</url></doc>
